				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Yes, the frame IRQ happened when 0x4017 was 0 (1 frame after powerup).
<br />
<br />The IRQ line stays hot until it's acknowledged, right ? eg.:
<br />- pending frame irq and pending mapper irq
<br />- acknowledge mapper irq
<br />- don't acknowledge frame irq
<br />- rti
<br />- pending frame irq again
<br />
<br />(loop)
<br />
<br />Writing 0x80 to 0x4017 won't acknowledge the pending IRQ (0x4017.6 does that).</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

